    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Dispatcher::addControllerDirectory() checks directories in the order that they were added.  On the other hand, Zend_Controller_RewriteRouter::route() matches routes in reverse.  Cascading (checking in reverse) seems more correct to me for directory routes.</p>

<p>---        foreach ($directories as $directory) {
